			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>First of all, good morning, you piles of pigshit.  Now that the salutations are out of the way, let me get down to my point:  Your stupid ideas won't work.  The people you're targeting are ordinary people, pawns.  The poor souls victimized yesterday were mostly visiting tourists from the Southern Hemisphere, and were not your enemies before, but their relatives and countrymen for sure don't like ISIS now, that's certain.<br />
 <br />
No, your dipshit ideas won't work because the people you're actually mad at, the ones who made the decisions that fucked up whatever you think got fucked up of yours, aren't riding bikes in the Park, nor are they in the crowd at music festivals, nor are they just getting to work at eight in the morning in a Trade Authority rental suite.<br />
 <br />
Like every other moron asshole coward sons of bitches, you went after soft targets because they were easy to get at, even though they had zero influence over our policy, and are considered disposable cogs by the very people you're actually pissed off at.  All you did was to sweep a few low-value pieces off some remote corner of the board, which, as you ought to know, any King or Queen would gladly sacrifice again and again to gain even the tiniest advantage for themselves.<br />
 <br />
Congratulations, you fools, you're succeeded in making yourselves universally hated forever.  No one will ever think of your kind as &quot;noble Partisans&quot; ever again, thanks to your laziness and your stinking fear of failure.  No one, including our own odious Elites has ever fucked your own causes as thoroughly as you have fucked them yourselves through your inhuman actions.<br />
 <br />
In conclusion, go fuck yourselves with a rusty exhaust pipe.</div>

